urdu transliteration text:
Tere Kaatil Mujhe, Rone Se Manaa Karte HainJabhi Roti Hun To A-bid Pe Sitam Karte HainKhul Ke Rowloon Mujhe, Naize Pe, Uthaalo Baba
They whip Imam Sajjad when I cry,
@HujjatELC

Naa Koi Mujhko Bulaa-ta Hai Sakina Keh KeShaam Ke Log Bulaa-te Hain Yateema Keh KeThokrain Khaati, Sakina Ko, Sambhaalo Baba
Sakina is falling, help me Baba
@HujjatELC

Baal Khenche Hain Mere, Mu Pe Tamaache MaareDekh Ke Ghazi Ke Sar, Ko Rahay Haste SaareHaiy Zarra Apna, Wafadaar, Jagaalo Baba
Wake up your loyal brother, O Baba
@HujjatELC
